\c 2
\s Jona anonyengetera ari mukati mehove
\p
\v 1 Ipapo Jona akanyengetera kuna Je- hovha Mwari wake ari mudumbu rehove.
\v 2 Akati, "Ndakadana kuna Jehovha ndiri munhamo yangu, Akandipindura;
\s Ndakadana ndiri mudumbu
\s reSheori,
\s Imi mukanzwa izwi rangu.
\p
\v 3 Nokuti makandikandira makadzika, mukati momwoyo wegungwa, Mvura zhinji yakanga
\s yandikomberedza;
\s Mafungu enyu namapoporodzi enyu akapfuura napamusoro pangu.
\p
\v 4 Ndikati, `Ndarashwa, hamuchandioni;'
\s Asi ndicharingirazve kuTemberi yenyu tsvene.
\p
\v 5 Mvura zhinji yakandikomberedza, kusvikira kumweya wangu; Pakadzika pakanga pandipoteredza; Maharanga akanga amonera
\s musoro wangu.
\p
\v 6 Ndakaburukira kumavambiso amakomo;
\p Nyika nezvipfigiso zvayo zvakandipfigiramo nokusingaperi; kunyange zvakadaro makabudisa upenyu hwangu pagomba, imi, Jehovha Mwari wangu.
\v 7 Mweya wangu wakati uchiziya mukati mangu,
\s ndikarangarira Jehovha; Munyengetero wangu ukapinda kwamuri muTemberi yenyu tsvene. Vanorangarira zvisina maturo
\s zvenhema
\s Vanorasha nyasha yavo.
\p
\v 9 Asi ndichakubayirai nezwi rokuvonga;
\s Ndicharipa zvandapika.
\p Ruponeso runobva kuna Jehovha."
\v 10 Jehovha akataura nehove, ikandorutsira Jona panyika yakaoma.
